extends base

block content 

    .page__hero.affiliate  
        .section__container 
            .page__head--text 
                h3.page--title Affiliate Resourse
                p.head--text We're excited to have you join us and start earning commissions by promoting our products and services. This get started guide will walk you through the process of becoming an affiliate and help you get up and running in no time.
                a.content__button(href="/signup") Become An Affiliate Now

    
    main 
        section.page__section
            .section__container
                h3.section__title Welcome to our affiliate program! 

                .get__started--content 
                    .content 
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/register.jpg", alt="")
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 1: Sign up as an Affiliate
                            p.section__description  To get started, you'll need to sign up for our affiliate program. Visit our website and look for the "Affiliate Program" or "Become an Affiliate" link. Click on it, and you'll be directed to the affiliate registration page. Fill out the required information, such as your name, contact details, and preferred payment method. Once you submit your application, our team will review it, and upon approval, you'll receive your unique affiliate ID and login details.
                    .content 
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 2: Familiarize Yourself with Our Products/Services
                            p.section__description  To effectively promote our products and services, it's essential to have a good understanding of what we offer. Take some time to explore our website, learn about our offerings, and identify the key features and benefits. This knowledge will enable you to create compelling content and answer any questions your audience may have.
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/familiarise.jpg", alt="")

                    .content 
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/promote_channel.jpg", alt="")
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 3: Choose Your Promotion Channels
                            p.section__description Consider the channels you have at your disposal to reach your audience. It could be your blog, website, social media platforms, email newsletters, or any other online medium. Think about where your target audience is most active and which channels will allow you to engage with them effectively. You can also experiment with different channels to find what works best for you.

                    .content 
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 4: Create Compelling Content
                            p.section__description Content is key when it comes to affiliate marketing. Develop engaging content that educates, entertains, or solves a problem for your audience. You can write product reviews, create informative blog posts, shoot engaging videos, or curate inspiring social media posts. Remember to incorporate your affiliate links naturally within your content to drive traffic to our website and track your referrals.
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/compelling.jpg", alt="")

                    .content 
                        //- img.content__image(src="../asset/img/track_performance.jpg", alt="")
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/track_performance2.jpg", alt="")
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 5: Track Your Performance
                            p.section__description We provide you with a comprehensive affiliate dashboard where you can track your performance in real-time. Monitor your clicks, conversions, and commission earnings to gauge the effectiveness of your promotional efforts. Use these insights to optimize your strategies and focus on the channels and content types that generate the best results.

                    .content 
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title Step 6: Engage with Your Audience
                            p.section__description Building a relationship with your audience is crucial for success as an affiliate. Respond to comments, messages, and inquiries promptly. Engage in discussions related to our products/services, and be a valuable resource for your audience. By establishing yourself as a trusted authority, you'll increase the likelihood of conversions and foster long-term loyalty.
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/audience2.jpeg", alt="")

                    .content 
                        img.content__image(src="../asset/img/relax.jpg", alt="")
                        .content__description 
                            h4.content__title  Step 7: Stay Updated and Evolve
                            p.section__description Keep an eye on our latest product launches, promotions, and updates. Stay informed about any changes to our affiliate program or commission structure. The affiliate marketing landscape is always evolving, so it's important to adapt your strategies accordingly. Attend webinars, read industry blogs, and stay connected with our affiliate program's newsletter to stay ahead of the curve.
                    
                    span 
                        p.section__description Remember, success in affiliate marketing takes time and effort. Be patient, persistent, and continuously learn from your experiences. We're here to support you along the way, so if you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our dedicated affiliate support team.
                        p.section__description Get started today and embark on an exciting journey as an affiliate partner with us. We look forward to helping you achieve your goals and rewarding you for your efforts!
                        a.content__button(href="/signup") Become An Affilliate Today
